column13: One potential change for 2023 would be rather than voting for books, one month would be assigned to each person who is interested, and they would have sole discretion over what book is chosen for that month. How do you feel about how the books should be chosen for 2023? Depending on how many people are interested, we'd try to assign months before January
column14: Also up for consideration is making one of the months a show & tell month. Rather than all reading the same book, we would all read our own and then tell the group about it. Or we could split off into pairs and each pair would read a separate book.
